\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Target or Area:}{\fs20\cf0  Object touched or up to 5 sq. ft./level
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Duration:}{\fs20\cf0  Permanent until discharged (D)
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Saving Throw:}{\fs20\cf0  See text
